+---------------------------------------------+-----------------------------------------------------------------------+-----------------------------------------------------------------+
| **Job Title**                               | **Core Skills**                                                       | **Preparation in MS Program**                                   |
+---------------------------------------------+-----------------------------------------------------------------------+-----------------------------------------------------------------+
